{"lastModified":1748864993937,"uri":"c::7819307041::vessel::721ce690-3b04-11f0-b870-8f0ec11a89b0","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Greece\n\nDesigned with leisure sailing and family enjoyment in mind, the BALI CATSMART effortlessly combines practicality with comfort. Whether you’re exploring tranquil waters or anchoring for quality family time, this boat is perfectly suited for both. The BALI CATSMART creates an inviting environment where relaxation and unforgettable moments take center stage.\n\nSmart and innovative\n\nStep aboard the BALI CATSMART and experience a new level of sailing pleasure. Immerse yourself in the smart and innovative features that have made the BALI range renowned. From the seamless integration of the “BALI door” to the functionality of the rigid forward cockpit, every aspect has been carefully designed to enhance your sailing experience.\n\nDiscover the Smart Spirit of the BALI CATSMART, a remarkable 38-foot catamaran that stays true to the DNA of the brand. With twin helm stations facilitating effortless sailing maneuvers and helming, the BALI CATSMART offers a sailing experience that is both enjoyable and user-friendly.","blueprint":{"name":"FILIPPOS III","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::721ce690-3b04-11f0-b870-8f0ec11a89b0::assets::3ce57a80-3b06-11f0-9af0-4d22c4844cb6/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::721ce690-3b04-11f0-b870-8f0ec11a89b0::assets::3cf224b0-3b06-11f0-9af0-4d22c4844cb6/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::721ce690-3b04-11f0-b870-8f0ec11a89b0::assets::3cff1d00-3b06-11f0-9af0-4d22c4844cb6/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::721ce690-3b04-11f0-b870-8f0ec11a89b0::assets::3ce6da10-3b06-11f0-9af0-4d22c4844cb6/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::721ce690-3b04-11f0-b870-8f0ec11a89b0::assets::3cebe320-3b06-11f0-9af0-4d22c4844cb6/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::721ce690-3b04-11f0-b870-8f0ec11a89b0::assets::3cf272d0-3b06-11